    <item>
      <title>🤖 AI That Explains Itself? Meet PJ-X! 🧐</title>
      <link>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/ai-explains-itself-pj-x/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://raf-97414.github.io/en/posts/ai-explains-itself-pj-x/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;-ai-that-explains-itself-meet-pj-x-&#34;&gt;📢 AI That Explains Itself? Meet PJ-X! 🧐&lt;a href=&#34;#-ai-that-explains-itself-meet-pj-x-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You know how people make bad decisions and then &lt;em&gt;try&lt;/em&gt; to explain them? AI does that too. Except this time, it’s actually useful.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;-whats-pj-x&#34;&gt;🤖 What’s PJ-X?&lt;a href=&#34;#-whats-pj-x&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pointing and Justification (PJ-X)&lt;/strong&gt; is an AI model that:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;✅ Makes decisions &lt;strong&gt;(like answering a question or identifying an action)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;✅ &lt;strong&gt;Explains its decision in plain English&lt;/strong&gt; (because &amp;ldquo;🤷‍♂️&amp;rdquo; isn&amp;rsquo;t acceptable)&lt;br&gt;&#xA;✅ &lt;strong&gt;Points to visual evidence&lt;/strong&gt; in an image (like a lawyer proving their case)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
